  "description": "HMAC-384/512 authentication engine using masked SHA-512 core with 12 LFSR entropy generators for side-channel resistance. Supports software-written keys and Caliptra CSR key input. KeyVault integration with 2 read ports and 1 write port. AHB-Lite slave interface. Extracted from CHIPS Alliance Caliptra Root of Trust.",
